gov.nih.nlm.meme.server
Interface ServerConstants

All Superinterfaces:
DataSourceConstants, MEMEConstants
All Known Subinterfaces:
ServerConstants
public interface ServerConstants
extends DataSourceConstants

This interface holds constants commonly used by the MEME server. It supplements the MEMEConstants. Most of the constants represent property names.

Author:
MEME Group

MEME_BOOTSTRAP

public static final String MEME_BOOTSTRAP
Property whose value will be a comma-separated list of fully-qualified names of classes implementing the Initializable interface. The classes in this list are initialized by the ServerToolkit.
